!! Features

* Show line numbers
* Highlight lines

Edit this tiddler to see how it works.

!! Demos

```js
// prism: {"line":"2"}

// We can even highlight lines:
console.log('Hello, JavaScript!');
```

```py
// prism: {"lineNumbers":false}

# Line numbers can be hidden
print('Hello, Python!')
```

